####################
# 创建评论测试
####################

### 4. 用户1对资源发表评论（顶级评论）
# @name createComment1
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "resource",
  "targetId": 1,
  "content": "这个资源非常有用，帮助我通过了考试！感谢分享。"
}

### 5. 用户2对同一资源发表评论
# @name createComment2
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "resource",
  "targetId": 1,
  "content": "同意楼上，这个资料整理得很详细，值得下载！"
}

### 6. 用户1回复用户2的评论（嵌套回复）
# @name createReply1
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "resource",
  "targetId": 1,
  "content": "是的，我也觉得整理得很好，特别是重点部分标注得很清楚。",
  "parentId": 2
}

### 7. 用户3也来回复用户2的评论
# @name createReply2
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token3}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "resource",
  "targetId": 1,
  "content": "确实不错，我已经下载了，很实用！",
  "parentId": 2
}

### 8. 用户2对问题发表评论
# @name createComment3
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "question",
  "targetId": 1,
  "content": "这个问题我也遇到过，建议先检查一下配置文件。"
}

### 9. 用户1对回答发表评论
# @name createComment4
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "answer",
  "targetId": 1,
  "content": "这个回答很详细，解决了我的疑惑！"
}

### 10. 用户3对活动发表评论
# @name createComment5
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token3}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "activity",
  "targetId": 1,
  "content": "这个活动很有意思，期待参加！"
}

