### 11. 创建评论 - 无效的父评论ID（应失败）
# @name createInvalidParent
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "resource",
  "targetId": 1,
  "content": "这是一个无效的回复",
  "parentId": 999999
}

### 12. 创建评论 - 缺少必填字段（应失败）
# @name createMissingField
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "resource",
  "targetId": 1
}

### 13. 创建评论 - 内容为空（应失败）
# @name createEmptyContent
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "resource",
  "targetId": 1,
  "content": ""
}

### 14. 创建评论 - 内容超长（应失败 - 超过1000字符）
# @name createOverLengthContent
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "resource",
  "targetId": 1,
  "content": "这是一段超过1000字符限制的测试内容用于验证Bean Validation注解是否正确生效END"
}

