Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 29. 用户1点赞评论2
# @name likeComment2
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment/2/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 30. 用户3也点赞评论1
# @name likeComment1ByUser3
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token3}}

