# @name likeCommentNotFound
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment/999999/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 33. 未登录点赞（应失败）
# @name likeCommentWithoutAuth
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment/1/like

####################
# 取消点赞测试
####################

