DELETE {{baseUrl}}/comment/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 35. 用户1取消点赞评论2
# @name unlikeComment2
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/comment/2/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

