# @name unlikeCommentNotFound
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/comment/999999/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 38. 未登录取消点赞（应失败）
# @name unlikeCommentWithoutAuth
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/comment/1/like

